question: Please provide me the patient associated with the claim transaction fdb84e8a-3e20-b3a8-0cf1-cea85c87cfd2.
answers:
```sql
SELECT p.FIRST || ' ' || p.LAST
FROM claims_transactions ct
JOIN claims c ON ct.CLAIMID = c.Id
JOIN patients p ON c.PATIENTID = p.Id
WHERE ct.CLAIMID = 'fdb84e8a-3e20-b3a8-0cf1-cea85c87cfd2';
```
